<span id="freeTextContainer6035880346502201931">Love the use of second person. Love feeling like I&apos;m hitting all the best parties in NYC. Love all the fun names for cocaine. I even love the twin towers depicted on the cover.<br/>Maybe a little short on plot and character but this is a fun novel not a sleep inducing, thought provoking, literary work.<br/><br/></span>
